cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.CY

This paper deals with the visualization of relationships between scientific publications, which is a common topic in the fields of digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), social networks (cs.SI), software development (cs.SD), and cybernetics (cs.CY). However, given the focus on citations and references, cs.DL and cs.IR are the most likely sub-categories.
